<section id="ddb-importer-muncher-sources" class="tab ddb-muncher {{ tab.cssClass }} {{#if tab.active}} active{{/if}}" data-tab="{{ tab.id }}" data-group="{{ tab.group }}">

    <fieldset>
    <legend>Excluded Flavour Profiles (Categories)</legend>
    <p>By default DDB Importer <strong>excludes</strong> third party categories from being imported.</p>
    <p>The following categories will be excluded. Please adjust to taste.</p>
    <p>Categories are used on D&D Beyond to filter content.
These are groups of books.
The 2024 PHB, MM and DMG are considered "Core Rules".
Expanded content are books like XGtE.
Legacy/non-core are books that were replaced in the 2014 ruleset lifecycle like Mordenkainenâ€™s Tome of Foes.</p>
    <div class="form-fields" id="munch-excluded-config">
      <multi-select id="muncher-excluded-source-categories" name="muncher-excluded-source-categories">
        {{#each excludedCategories}}
        <option value="{{this.id}}" {{this.selected}}> {{this.label}}</option>
        {{/each}}
      </multi-select>
    </div>
    </fieldset>

</section>
